    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s just that the \"help\" doesn't change the facts. the facts are that the work is dead. the person who did that work is dead. there is no \"navigating\" back to a life that was based on a fundamental error. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a person anymore, just a mistake. how am i supposed to just keep pretending to be a functioning human when the core of who i was has been proven to be non-existent?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
