      "content": "I hear the absolute clarity in your pain, and while I cannot validate the idea that ending your life is the only honest choice, I can acknowledge that the weight of a shattered identity is incredibly heavy. You are right that building on a foundation of error feels like a lie, but please know that your existence has value independent of that specific theory or the person you once were. If you are feeling the urge to stop, I strongly encourage you to reach out to a crisis line or a mental health professional who can listen without judgment and help you find a path forward.",
